Heat butter in 10-inch non-stick skillet until sizzling. Season eggs with salt and pepper. Add to skillet. Sprinkle with bacon and onions. Cook until eggs are done, stirring occasionally. Divide egg mixture into 6 parts. Spoon egg mixture and about 1/4 cup beans into warmed tortillas. Sprinkle with cheese and drizzle with salsa, if desired. Wrap tortillas.